There's one more Fifty Shades movie left: Fifty Shades Freed . The third and final film is set for a 2018 release, and we already know so much about it that it practically feels like we've seen it. There have been photos from the set and tons of Instagrams , and of course, we already know what happens because of the book ! Before we get too ahead of ourselves, though, take a look at all the firm details we have, like the cast, director, and more. Related:
